# get_irida_analysis_submissions_by_type
# get all analysis submissions of a given type
# TYPE is one of: phylogenomics, assembly, sistr
#
# WARNING: this endpoint queries Galaxy directly. it is SLOW.
# expect 15-60 seconds or more depending on the number of analyses.
#
# example: get_irida_analysis_submissions_by_type assembly
